{"tid":1003380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人口超承載致社會全面爆煲　要求政府減少單程證紓緩問題　聯署","createTime":"2019-01-31T15:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T08:23:21.000Z","uid":47714,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"35ea61453ae9468004afe2f8f64f4d9e0517001f","tid":1003380,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:06:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/population.hongkong/posts/2266679756730170\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpopulation.hongkong%2Fposts%2F2266679756730170&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=e76227f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/population.hongkong/posts/2266679756730170</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/jZxfVXRCnGFxKkmA3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FjZxfVXRCnGFxKkmA3&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FYTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=4c60747b\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/jZxfVXRCnGFxKkmA3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://is.gd/N54KKb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FN54KKb&h=b1e8d050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【聯署目的】<br />\n要求政府減少單程證，紓緩醫療、房屋及社會福利等社會問題<br />\n<br />\n【聯署內文】<br />\n政府長期漠視移民來港對社會構成的影響，近日公立醫院的專業醫護人士集會訴苦，指病房長期爆滿，工作瘋狂超時又承受巨大壓力，要求當局正視醫療系統已臨崩潰，就是不可迴避、須立即收緊人口遷入的警號。<br />\n<br />\n超負荷的人口其實亦將其他多項公共服務和資源推至臨界點，包括香港近年極為嚴峻的住屋問題。為安頓新增人口，政府部門則到處搶地開發，直接導致「盲搶地」、「人工島」及是否發展郊野公園等土地規劃爭議，使香港上下爭吵不安。<br />\n<br />\n社會承載力有其極限，香港實在難以消化大量單程證所衍生的房屋及醫療需求。我等呼籲社會理性認清減少輸入人口的必要，更促請政府認真面對問題源頭，回應港人長期以來參與單程證審批權，削減配額的強烈訴求。<br />\n<br />\n【聯署時期】<br />\n2019年2月1日至3月31日<br />\n<br />\n【發起團體】<br />\n人口政策關注組"},{"pid":"1dda39de9e442096c5850c20c5b086a4af0fa028","tid":1003380,"uid":216421,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街政府"},{"pid":"9dd3ef41016ac533444587d66e9fe02be9a9b35d","tid":1003380,"uid":5499,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:14:36.000Z","msg":"政府一定唔會理, 佢個目的就係要搞成咁"},{"pid":"546febc27d1f8eaa4d2e0ef777987190a5e4f085","tid":1003380,"uid":54940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"signed<br />\n<br />\n雖然知就算有七百萬人簽都唔會有用"},{"pid":"7632c1fb2475c57a215985094cd9e4abfe26ccc0","tid":1003380,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"signed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f3d44b2c592f41b5c5dcdf016025fdd97dbc60","tid":1003380,"uid":163111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:07:50.000Z","msg":"signed + 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3743d1d38fd4782ccc7aa649c202a0e385737bb","tid":1003380,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:08:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"046f5cf411c06aa109b0bd0f33a7f114ab098610","tid":1003380,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:09:26.000Z","msg":"signed 停止支那人來港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c61370e356fa35e1d26ae839302284f646357a4","tid":1003380,"uid":113007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:17:38.000Z","msg":"睇都唔撚睇呀，d議員又垃圾"},{"pid":"aa419374f95627b26285d03b59818ee64a120063","tid":1003380,"uid":49370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T20:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b63c045f59022515bb7b993c2851c7d1a7ee8a0","tid":1003380,